### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api
@contentType = application/json
@authToken = your-jwt-token-here

### Get All Notifications
GET {{baseUrl}}/notifications
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get All Notifications - Filter Unread
GET {{baseUrl}}/notifications?isRead=false
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get All Notifications - Filter Read
GET {{baseUrl}}/notifications?isRead=true
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get Unread Notifications Count
GET {{baseUrl}}/notifications/unread-count
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get Notification by ID
@notificationId = 1
GET {{baseUrl}}/notifications/{{notificationId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get Notification by ID - Invalid ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/notifications/invalid-id
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get Notification by ID - Not Found
GET {{baseUrl}}/notifications/9999
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Mark Notification as Read
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/notifications/1/read
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Mark Notification as Read - Not Found
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/notifications/9999/read
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Mark All Notifications as Read
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/notifications/mark-all-read
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Delete Notification
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/notifications/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Delete Notification - Not Found
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/notifications/9999
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Delete Notification - Unauthorized (another user's notification)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/notifications/10
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
